  "title": "Inside Sales Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ol>\n  <li>Independently manage commercial tasks during the bidding process, including but not limited to requirement confirmation, project cost collection, and quotation preparation.</li>\n  <li>Track project implementation progress, coordinating with relevant departments to resolve issues arising during execution.</li>\n  <li>Support project reconciliation, acceptance, and payment collection processes.</li>\n  <li>Compile and report project data on a regular basis.</li>\n  <li>Handle client-side communication and coordination on business-related matters.</li>\n  <li>Assist supervisors with other assigned duties as needed.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ol>\n  <li>Prior experience in a business or commercial support role is preferred.</li>\n  <li>Proficient in Microsoft Office and other office software; possesses basic network knowledge and strong document editing skills.</li>\n  <li>Positive and proactive attitude, with strong analytical, communication, and coordination abilities. Detail-oriented, responsible, adaptable, and service-minded.</li>\n  <li>Able to work under pressure and willing to perform reasonable overtime when required.</li>\n</ol>",
