    "description": "<p>EZSVS SINGAPORE(PTE.) LTD. is wholly owned by EZSVS Co., Ltd. (EZSVS), a leading internet data center (IDC) service provider in China and a long-term partner of leading Chinese internet companies including Baidu, Alibaba, and Tencent.</p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p>Established in March 2005, EZSVS provides data center engineering service to customers. “EZ” means easy for customers and “SVS” means service. Just like the name indicates, EZSVS has been providing a full range of superior data center services to customers and make their lives easy.</p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p>For more than a decade, EZSVS formed its core value: sincerity, simplicity, excellence, and privilege. In the last several years, EZSVS grows rapidly and leading enterprises to support their global data center operation.</p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p>As the extension of EZSVS in Singapore, EZSVS provides engineering in data centers service to customers in Singapore. Its businesses include IT system integration, training of data center service, hardware installation/ relocation/ post-sales services, and data center operation.</p>\n",
